#

Creamy Shrimp Bisque with Garlic and Herb Croutons

$12.99
350 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

ShellfishDairy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeDairy-Free

Tags:

SeafoodSoupComfort Food

Description

A rich and velvety shrimp bisque, served with crispy garlic and herb croutons for a delightful crunch.

Ingredients

  • Shrimp (peeled and deveined): 1 lb
  • Butter: 2 tbsp
  • Shallots (finely chopped): 1
  • Garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • Tomato paste: 2 tbsp
  • Chicken stock: 4 cups
  • Heavy cream: 1 cup
  • Fresh thyme leaves: 1 tbsp
  • Bay leaf: 1
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
  • Crusty bread (for croutons): 2 cups
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Parsley (chopped): 2 tbsp
